<br>
In a group, air pet (or 52+ fire) is the best.  Once you debuff the mob (malaise etc.) his stuns will keep the group's tank from getting hurt near as much and so the healer will have more mana.<br>
<br>
That's my 2c.  Probably colored a lot by use of the 50+ pets though, so take it with a grain of salt.  I do recall using the earth primarily for a LONG time though.<br>
